          }
        ],
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The talisman teleports you to a clear space of your choice that you can see within 120 feet. This also transports any items you're wearing and holding with you, as well as up to one other creature currently in contact with you\u2014including if you're carrying it in an extradimensional container. This effect has the teleportation trait.",
        "type": "stat_block"
